cc:Work.dc:title: Funny Chick Cartoon Newborn Coming Out from the Egg with a Chocolate Eggshell hat
cc:Work.dc:description: Funny Chick Cartoon Newborn Coming Out from the Egg with a Chocolate Eggshell hat - Drôle de poussin nouveau né dans son oeuf avec chapeau en coquille d'oeuf en chocolat - Lustige neugeborenen Küken in seinem Ei mit Schokolade Eierschale Hut - Pulcino divertente neonato nel suo uovo e con un cappello in guscio d'uovo di cioccolata (partially remixed from "Martouf" and "rg1024" illustrations)
